snippet.title: Songbird Symphony - Musical Trailer
snippet.description:
A heart-warming journey of discovery, as orphaned chick 'Birb' sets off to find his true origins.

In Songbird Symphony, you are able to influence the background music with your puzzle-solving skills! The more creatures of the forest's different chapters you help out on your way, the more musical elements are added to the background until the perfect symphony is unlocked.

Connecting the movement of platforms, doors and many other elements, that Birb has to overcome on his journey, with rhythmic inputs, the game offers a new way to enjoy classic jump'n'run gameplay! Listen closely to the background music, become one with the symphony of the forest and hit the right buttons at the right time to fly through the singing, dancing levels of Songbird Symphony!

Flying onto Nintendo Switch, Playstation 4 and Steam July 25th!
